TableToExcelClient - Class in com.googlecode.gwtTableToExcel.client
Build a Form Panel in order to allow to download the table content in an excel format.
Dont forget to add an iframe in your original html file :
< iframe src="javascript:''" id="gwt-table-to-excel-target" class="invisible">< /iframe>
and to declare the sevlet in your web.xml :

TableToExcelServlet - Class in com.googlecode.gwtTableToExcel.server
Servlet which do the magic conversion.
Dont forget to declare it in your web.xml
< servlet>
< servlet-name>gwtTableToExcelServlet< /servlet-name>
< servlet-class>com.googlecode.gwtTableToExcel.server.TableToExcelServlet< /servlet-class>

< servlet-mapping>
< servlet-name>gwtTableToExcelServlet< /servlet-name>
< url-pattern>/gtte/gtte< /url-pattern>
< /servlet-mapping>
